ygData.messageBody:
LOL, I got LD last night too, go back to the char screen and noticed my wiz
drop 1 lvl. Reboot system after 3 failure to ener EQ world. Luckily when
I relogin EQ, I'm back to lvl 6 (ok I know I'm slow, been playing MW3 over
gaming zone last weekend, heh).

Btw, Eriz (Paladin) and Kell (Enchanter) is now with me at Ak'Anon hunting
skeleton. The skeleton here con red/yellow to us. Nice xp when we got a
group of 4 (including a healer). Hopefully tonight we can make a
tank/buffer/healer/blaster team again and earn xp ;)

Mondain
